corsets.name: Green corset
corsets.description: A spectacular mini dress with a fitted cut,made in a rich terracotta shade.The model emphasizes the silhouette, accentuating the waist and smooth lines of the figure.There is a flirty silt in front,adding a bold touch, and a row of silver buttons gives the image a noble shine and makes it especially expressive.The perfect choice for an evening out or a stylish party.
